00:59:58.010 --> 01:00:01.770
And we can actually
calculate that

01:00:01.770 --> 01:00:06.840
by evaluating the phase
difference between the path

01:00:06.840 --> 01:00:09.780
number one and the
path number two.

01:00:09.780 --> 01:00:15.030
So now, in order to have
constructive interference,

01:00:15.030 --> 01:00:18.420
I need a specific
phase difference.

01:00:18.420 --> 01:00:22.310
But before that, I need to
calculate the phase difference

01:00:22.310 --> 01:00:32.100
first between path number
one and path number two.

01:00:32.100 --> 01:00:35.430
What will be the
